<!-- EDIT3 SECTION "Example of a pure animation (No directional frames) image:" [1170-1272] -->
<h2 class="sectionedit4"><a name="example_of_a_pure_directional_image" id="example_of_a_pure_directional_image">Example of a pure directional image:</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
The angle ranges will be calculated automatically from the amount of rows the image has, the more rows the thinner the range will be.
</p>

<p>
The image displays for which angle ranges each frame will be shown.
</p>

<p>
<a href="http://gusanos.sourceforge.net/documentation/doku/lib/exe/detail.php?id=main%3Amodding_docs%3Asprites&amp;media=gusimages:directionalex.png" class="media wikilink2" title="gusimages:directionalex.png"><img src="http://gusanos.sourceforge.net/documentation/doku/lib/exe/fetch.php?media=gusimages:directionalex.png" class="media" alt="" /></a>
</p>

</div>
